Packages 
Package Description
com.jpn.bowling
Application base package with @SpringBootApplication and CommandLineRunner for command line execution of this application
com.jpn.bowling.components
All specific bowling components interfaces are located here
com.jpn.bowling.components.impl
All specific implementations of bowling or game components interfaces are located here
com.jpn.bowling.components.score
Components implementations of related to bowling score calculation
com.jpn.bowling.domain
Classes that represents different objects of the bowling scoreboard domain
com.jpn.bowling.exceptions
Custom exceptions for each bowling fault scenario
com.jpn.bowling.input
Provides required classes for user input interaction
com.jpn.games.components
Generic interfaces for any game that needs to compute or process scores
com.jpn.games.domain
Generic base objects for any game that needs to compute or process scores
com.jpn.games.exceptions
Generic exception for any game that needs to compute or process scores
